    "body": "Problem: Since the \"[Process exited]\" msg is no longer part of buffer contents, `jobstart`'s reuse of unmodified finished terminal buffers does not clear the msg. This may cause issues like [#37987 (comment)](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/37987#issuecomment-4035282992)\r\n\r\nSolution: Delete the extmark if `term` is already closed.",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-11T09:13:39Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
                    "href": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38246#discussion_r2916677083"
