                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/comments/2916677083"
                }
            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It seems that you need to move this to the `if (term->closed)` branch above, as `close_cb` can free the terminal immediately.",
